Extension to trigger build autopilot (jenkins) with parameter.
Guild: 
1.Get Jenkins token
 - Goto https://autopilot.shopbase.dev/user/[Your_email]/configure.
- Choose Add new token.
- Save the token.
- Clone Project & extract

2. Build
- Open extension
- Enter user, token
- Enter path, test cases,...
- Click build.
